Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Iran-Contra scandal revealed, 1986
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydpf1
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 21 Nov 1986
America reacts to revelations of a US arms for hostages deal with Iran. Arbitrageur Ivan Boesky admits insider trading on Wall Street and is fined $100 million.